                <note rend="inline" type="source">838.77/220: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The High Commissioner in Haiti</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Russell</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Port au Prince</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1923-03-09T16:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 9, 1923—4 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/>[Received March 10—10:35 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>30. President Borno has this morning informed me that he approves of plan of
                    reorganization [of] National Railroad. …</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Russell</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
